message.content: cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CC. The paper deals with factoid question answering, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP) and information retrieval (IR). The paper also discusses the use of crowdsourcing, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (AI) research. The paper also presents results achieved by state-of-the-art systems, which is a common theme in machine learning (ML) and computational linguistics (CL) research. Finally, the paper discusses the construction of a large dataset, which is relevant to data mining (DM) and database (DB) research.
